def test_home_status_change(self):
        try:
            # 初始化发现页操作类（传入self即可复用所有minium对象）
            home_page = HomePage(self)

            # 链式调用公共方法，逻辑清晰
            home_page.goto_home_page()

            self.page.wait_for(
                lambda: self.page.element_is_exists(home_myhome_element, max_timeout=max_timeout),
                max_timeout=max_timeout)
            time.sleep(3)

            current_status_list = self.page.get_elements(home_tab_current_status_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
            current_status = current_status_list[0]

            # 判断当前状态 如果是休闲 切换为 商务
            if current_status.attribute("src")[0] == home_tab_friendship_src:

                self.logger.info(f"当前广场状态为：{home_tab_title_friendship_name}")
                self.capture(f"当前广场状态为{home_tab_title_friendship_name}_{time.strftime("%H%M%S")}")

                # 点击广场 tab
                home_tab = self.page.get_element(selector=home_tab_tag, inner_text=home_tab_inner_text,
                                                 max_timeout=max_timeout)
                home_tab.tap()
                time.sleep(1)

                current_status_list = self.page.get_elements(home_tab_current_status_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
                current_status = current_status_list[0]

                if current_status.attribute("src")[0] == home_tab_business_src:
                    self.logger.info(f"当前广场状态已更改为：{home_tab_title_business_name}")
                    self.capture(f"广场状态已切换为{home_tab_title_business_name}_{time.strftime("%H%M%S")}")
                else:
                    self.logger.info(f"广场状态切换失败，当前为：{home_tab_title_friendship_name}")
                    self.capture(f"广场状态切换失败，当前为{home_tab_title_friendship_name}_{time.strftime("%H%M%S")}")

            # 判断当前状态 如果是商务 切换为 休闲
            elif current_status.attribute("src")[0] == home_tab_business_src:

                self.logger.info(f"当前广场状态为：{home_tab_title_business_name}")
                self.capture(f"当前广场状态为{home_tab_title_business_name}_{time.strftime("%H%M%S")}")

                # 点击广场 tab
                home_tab = self.page.get_element(selector=home_tab_tag, inner_text=home_tab_inner_text,
                                                 max_timeout=max_timeout)
                home_tab.tap()
                time.sleep(1)

                current_status_list = self.page.get_elements(home_tab_current_status_element, max_timeout=max_timeout)
                current_status = current_status_list[0]

                if current_status.attribute("src")[0] == home_tab_friendship_src:
                    self.logger.info(f"当前广场状态已更改为：{home_tab_title_friendship_name}")
                    self.capture(f"广场状态已切换为{home_tab_title_friendship_name}_{time.strftime("%H%M%S")}")
                else:
                    self.logger.info(f"广场状态切换失败，当前为：{home_tab_title_business_name}")
                    self.capture(f"广场状态切换失败，当前为{home_tab_title_business_name}_{time.strftime("%H%M%S")}")


        except Exception as e:
            self.logger.error(f"广场切换状态失败：{str(e)}")
            # 异常时截图
            timestamp = time.strftime("%H%M%S")
            self.capture(f"广场切换状态失败_{timestamp}")
            raise

        time.sleep(2)
